snippet.title: Greatest Common Factor Trick GCF
snippet.description:
It is easy to find the greatest common factor using this old method.  This is the fastest method of working out greatst common factors short of knowing all the factors for every number!
This method works rapidly evenforlarge numbers and utilises the Euclidean algorithm.  Big shoutout to Nicki - thanks for your comment! To donate to the tecmath channel:  https://paypal.me/tecmath?locale.x=en_AU
